<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 10:07:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军参与加沙地带南部和北部；在美国的推动下，以色列提供更多燃料</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-live/under-u-s-pressure-israeli-cabinet-approves-more-fuel-for-gaza/0000018c-4281-db23-ad9f-6ad9e0600000</link><description>以色列国防军继续在加沙地带北部和南部推进地面行动 ■ 以色列国防军公布了周三在加沙战斗中丧生的两名士兵的名字 ■ 《纽约时报》报道，美国司法部正在调查 10 月 7 日哈马斯谋杀 30 多名美国公民的事件 ■ 欧盟外交博雷尔部长和世卫组织总干事表示支持联合国秘书长古特雷斯援引第99条。 ■ 自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,200名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 138 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,899 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-live/under-u-s-pressure-israeli-cabinet-approves-more-fuel-for-gaza/0000018c-4281-db23-ad9f-6ad9e0600000</guid></item><item><title>拜登热衷于让以色列在加沙对哈马斯发动攻势，但设定了明确的价格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-allowing-israels-gaza-offensive-to-proceed-but-with-a-price/0000018c-40f3-d245-a38c-cbf3afc70000</link><description>美国对以色列行动的支持似乎取决于提供人道主义援助 ■ 人质家属警告说，随着以色列国防军将攻势扩大到加沙地带南部，战斗正冒着他们亲人的生命危险</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-allowing-israels-gaza-offensive-to-proceed-but-with-a-price/0000018c-40f3-d245-a38c-cbf3afc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-黎巴嫩缓冲区？短期内不会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-lebanon-buffer-zone-not-anytime-soon/0000018c-40f2-d868-addd-d0f26ed00000</link><description>以色列推动真主党与其北部边境保持距离。黎巴嫩在目前的政治体制下几乎无法在任何问题上做出决定，更不用说保护边界等重大问题了</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:27:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-lebanon-buffer-zone-not-anytime-soon/0000018c-40f2-d868-addd-d0f26ed00000</guid></item><item><title>犹太大屠杀纪念馆对大学校长“借口”对犹太人进行种族灭绝的呼吁感到“震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/yad-vashem-appalled-by-university-presidents-excusing-calls-for-genocide-against-jews/0000018c-4154-d868-addd-d1f454750000</link><description>大屠杀纪念活动主席将美国精英大学校长的证词描述为“对历史的基本无知”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 00:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/yad-vashem-appalled-by-university-presidents-excusing-calls-for-genocide-against-jews/0000018c-4154-d868-addd-d1f454750000</guid></item><item><title>大学校长回避有关种族灭绝犹太人呼吁的问题后，白宫感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/white-house-outraged-as-college-presidents-skirt-questions-on-calls-for-genocide-of-jews/0000018c-40f5-db23-ad9f-68fde0de0000</link><description>众议院共和党人从一开始的意图就是公开嘲笑大学校长。即使考虑到这种背景，总统们还是成功地平息了美国犹太社区的疏远和激怒。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 21:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/white-house-outraged-as-college-presidents-skirt-questions-on-calls-for-genocide-of-jews/0000018c-40f5-db23-ad9f-68fde0de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最新预算首次投票通过，部长们批评非战争开支</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-updated-budget-passes-in-first-vote-as-ministers-criticize-non-war-expenses/0000018c-40d0-d868-addd-d0f00b960000</link><description>在没有利库德集团部长尼尔·巴尔卡特和约夫·加兰特以及部长本尼·甘茨的支持的情况下，以色列议会在所需的三轮投票中的第一轮就通过了预算的更新版本</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 21:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-updated-budget-passes-in-first-vote-as-ministers-criticize-non-war-expenses/0000018c-40d0-d868-addd-d0f00b960000</guid></item><item><title>这就是生与死：武装以色列平民是一项可怕的安全政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/thats-life-and-death-arming-israeli-civilians-is-a-terrible-security-policy/0000018c-40a5-db23-ad9f-68fd78bd0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日袭击事件以来，以色列已收到超过 25 万份新枪支许可证申请，这一数字超过了过去 20 年的总和。数据表明，这不会让国家变得更安全——相反</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 20:33:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/thats-life-and-death-arming-israeli-civilians-is-a-terrible-security-policy/0000018c-40a5-db23-ad9f-68fd78bd0000</guid></item><item><title>寻找一位国会拥护者来对抗反犹太主义？忘记斯特凡尼克</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-06/ty-article/.highlight/looking-for-a-congressional-champion-to-fight-antisemitism-forget-stefanik/0000018c-3feb-d062-a9ee-ffeb4d050000</link><description>那些担心反犹太主义的人最好记住，他们的新主要倡导者已经提出了一些最卑鄙的反犹太主义阴谋论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 18:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-06/ty-article/.highlight/looking-for-a-congressional-champion-to-fight-antisemitism-forget-stefanik/0000018c-3feb-d062-a9ee-ffeb4d050000</guid></item><item><title>夹在哈马斯和真主党之间，内塔尼亚胡失败的政府不会有任何进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/stuck-between-hamas-and-hezbollah-netanyahus-failed-government-isnt-going-anywhere/0000018c-3f84-dede-a7dd-3fc582b40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理的联盟陷入了一个循环：立法者表达了他们的反对意见，但随后投票支持总理 ■ 在甘茨离开联盟之前，没有人会越界，但只要人质仍被扣押在以色列，他就不会这样做。加沙</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 17:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/stuck-between-hamas-and-hezbollah-netanyahus-failed-government-isnt-going-anywhere/0000018c-3f84-dede-a7dd-3fc582b40000</guid></item><item><title>没有设备、人员或电力：加沙地带南部的医院因伤病人数过多而不堪重负</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</link><description>汗尤尼斯和拉法医院的医生告诉《国土报》，当地情况不断恶化，床位和物资匮乏，并且有可能爆发疾病，导致死亡人数飙升。如果疏散迫在眉睫，医生会问：“我们要去哪里？”我们可以将病人疏散到哪里？</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 15:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙地带的空袭将巴勒斯坦人推至埃及边境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airstrikes-in-gaza-strip-push-palestinians-to-egyptian-border/0000018c-3f44-d826-ab9e-bfdfe3040000</link><description>来自加沙北部的数十万难民目前在南部避难 ■ 战争专家称，尽管拜登警告以色列要更加努力不要伤害平民，但以色列在加沙的行动似乎没有重大变化</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 14:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airstrikes-in-gaza-strip-push-palestinians-to-egyptian-border/0000018c-3f44-d826-ab9e-bfdfe3040000</guid></item><item><title>大屠杀并不能证明大屠杀是正当的：以色列、加沙和战争罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/massacre-doesnt-justify-massacre-israel-gaza-and-war-crimes/0000018c-3585-d55e-adbf-7fd7c8900000</link><description>攻击我的《纽约时报》专栏文章的一群历史学家对以色列政策做出了令人尴尬的道歉，但没有谴责大量加沙平民死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 14:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/massacre-doesnt-justify-massacre-israel-gaza-and-war-crimes/0000018c-3585-d55e-adbf-7fd7c8900000</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯囚禁条件合理的假设不再存在”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/the-assumption-that-hamas-captivity-conditions-are-reasonable-no-longer-exists/0000018c-3edd-d8ec-a79c-ffff22f60000</link><description>代表 10 月 7 日在加沙被绑架的以色列人家属的医疗小组的负责人哈盖·莱文 (Hagai Levine) 教授对其余人质的状况表示严重担忧。 “如果以色列战时内阁认为人质有时间，那就错了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 13:38:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/the-assumption-that-hamas-captivity-conditions-are-reasonable-no-longer-exists/0000018c-3edd-d8ec-a79c-ffff22f60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列顶级讽刺电视节目嘲笑联合国未能谴责哈马斯的性犯罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/israels-top-satirical-tv-show-mocks-un-failure-to-condemn-hamas-sexual-crimes/0000018c-3ecd-d826-ab9e-bfdf90490000</link><description>在联合国关于“有预谋和有计划的”哈马斯性暴力的第一届特别会议之后发布的一个短剧中，以色列相当于《周六夜现场》的节目中，联合国妇女署通讯调查的两名代表向一位身份不明的对话者保证他们“相信你”</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 13:16:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/israels-top-satirical-tv-show-mocks-un-failure-to-condemn-hamas-sexual-crimes/0000018c-3ecd-d826-ab9e-bfdf90490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列“箭”系统拦截从也门发射的第四枚伊朗弹道导弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-arrow-system-downs-fourth-iranian-missile-launched-from-yemen/0000018c-3f1c-d53d-a7fc-bfbd2c4e0000</link><description>自加沙与哈马斯战争爆发以来，伊朗支持的胡塞武装向以色列发射了多枚导弹和无人机，距离超过1500公里，并击中了红海的以色列船只</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 13:06:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-arrow-system-downs-fourth-iranian-missile-launched-from-yemen/0000018c-3f1c-d53d-a7fc-bfbd2c4e0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登仍然支持以色列加沙战争，但限制其范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/biden-still-supports-israels-gaza-war-but-limits-its-scope/0000018c-3e99-d826-ab9e-bf9fc5a60000</link><description>以色列战时内阁已同意美国的要求，例如允许向加沙提供更多人道主义援助，包括燃料，并接受对以色列国防军在加沙地带南部行动规模的某些限制。主要分歧点涉及加沙“后天”计划的问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 12:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/biden-still-supports-israels-gaza-war-but-limits-its-scope/0000018c-3e99-d826-ab9e-bf9fc5a60000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击后，越来越多的美国中东学者进行自我审查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/growing-number-of-u-s-based-mideast-scholars-self-censoring-after-oct-7-hamas-attack/0000018c-3eb9-d826-ab9e-bfbfcc820000</link><description>自以色列与哈马斯战争开始以来实行自我审查的人中，81% 的人表示他们不会批评以色列，而只有 11% 的人不会批评巴勒斯坦人。对冒犯学生的担忧和来自外部倡导团体的压力被认为是主要原因</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 12:15:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/growing-number-of-u-s-based-mideast-scholars-self-censoring-after-oct-7-hamas-attack/0000018c-3eb9-d826-ab9e-bfbfcc820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军为加沙巴勒斯坦人绘制的令人困惑且具有讽刺意味的疏散地图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/the-idfs-confusing-ironic-evacuation-map-for-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018c-3b63-de12-a3af-3bef79640000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，该地图将加沙地带划分为 623 个区域，目前正用于指导加沙南部的巴勒斯坦人如何避开危险地区，是尽量减少平民伤亡的关键工具。虽然它是半个世纪前首次制定的</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/the-idfs-confusing-ironic-evacuation-map-for-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018c-3b63-de12-a3af-3bef79640000</guid></item><item><title>现在鹰嘴豆泥被要求参加以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/now-hummus-is-called-to-battle-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-39a5-d11b-a3bf-ffadaab60000</link><description>一份围绕美国食品行业的请愿书将以色列美食视为冲突的主要原因之一。但烹饪领域的文化挪用从一开始就存在问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/now-hummus-is-called-to-battle-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-39a5-d11b-a3bf-ffadaab60000</guid></item><item><title>巨大的弹坑、儿童死亡、房屋倒塌：加沙南部无处可逃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/huge-craters-dead-children-collapsed-homes-in-southern-gaza-theres-nowhere-to-flee/0000018c-3e77-d8ec-a79c-ffff72000000</link><description>轰炸的恢复正在将加沙人进一步向南推向拉法，那里有一百万流离失所者生活在拥挤不堪的环境中。人们因食物和水供应不足而互相争斗，而警察则试图维持一定程度的秩序</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:22:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/huge-craters-dead-children-collapsed-homes-in-southern-gaza-theres-nowhere-to-flee/0000018c-3e77-d8ec-a79c-ffff72000000</guid></item></channel></rss>